high_descs: Turn right, hang a left at the wall and walk to the black container on the floor next to the fridge ahead.
Pick up the green sponge on the left from inside the black container on the floor.
Turn around, take a right and walk to the counter on the left.
Put the green sponge inside the silver pot in the middle of the counter.
Pick up the pot with the sponge inside on the counter.
Turn right and walk to the sink on the right.
Put the pot with the sponge inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a pot with a sponge in a sink.

high_descs: Turn to the right, go to the wall, hang a left, go to the garbage can.
Pick up the leftmost sponge from inside the garbage can.
Turn around, go forward, hang a right, go to the counter on the left where the pot is.
Put the sponge inside the pot on the counter.
Pick up the pot containing the sponge from the counter.
Turn to the right, go to the sink that is ahead on the right.
Put the pot in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot containing a sponge in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right walk forward then turn left head to the trash bin beside the fridge
Pick up the sponge in the trash bin
Turn left then turn right walk forward then face the kitchen island
Put the sponge in the pot
Pick up the pot on the kitchen island
Turn right then head to the sink
Put the pot with sponge in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the pot with sponge in the sink
